Package com.upsight.android.internal.persistence.storable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StorableIdentifierAccessor
    Defines an API for writing and reading an identifier from an object Class.
    StorableIdFactory
    This interface defines a contract between the data store and the component responsible to generate object IDs which abstracting the generation process.
    StorableTypeAccessor<T>
    Defines an API to access the type of a class annotated with com.upsight.android.persistence.annotation.UpsightStorableType.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultJsonSerializer<T>
    Default implementation of UpsightJsonSerializer that will serialize a class based on it's class structure.
    StorableInfo<T>
    This class contains all the information required to internally manage classes annotated with UpsightStorableType.
    StorableInfoCache
    Caches all internal information required to manage the UpsightStorableType classes.
    StorableModule
    Package module.
    Storables
    Factory class for UpsightStorable operators.
